data.description: PAID OFF SOLAR! NO HOA! Welcome to 1034 Haviture Way! This immaculate, move-in ready 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 2103 square foot single-story gem is a 2020 build, offering modern living at its finest. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting open concept layout that seamlessly blends the living and dining areas, creating a sense of spaciousness and warmth. The large kitchen, equipped with modern appliances, is a chef's delight, perfect for preparing meals and entertaining friends and family. This home boasts three spacious bedrooms, but the real highlight is the expansive private owners suite located at the back of the home. It's your personal retreat, complete with an en-suite bathroom and ample space for relaxation and rest. The interior is adorned with wood-like vinyl flooring and plush carpeting throughout, offering a perfect balance of style and comfort. Both bathrooms have been thoughtfully upgraded, adding a touch of luxury to your daily routine. One of the standout features of this property is the fully paid-off solar system.  No HOA dues and lower taxes only sweeten the deal, making this home a savvy investment. Situated on a corner lot, this home offers added privacy, and the backyard is a blank canvas for your creativity and landscaping ideas. Imagine outdoor gatherings, gardening, or a relaxing oasis - the choice is yours. The location is another reason to fall in love with this home. Conveniently situated near parks, schools, shopping, dining, and beautiful mountain views, you'll have everything you need right at your doorstep.  There's no better time than now to make this house your new home. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity and make 1034 Haviture Way your home and "Have it Your Way"!  Let's open escrow today so you can spend the new year in your new home!
